  The Zee Cine Award or "ZCA" for short is an  
  awards ceremony for the Hindi film industry. 
  The awards were inaugurated in 1998 and are a
  mixture of categories decided on by public   
  votes,as well as categories solely judged by 
  an industry jury.Since then,it has gained    
  substantial popularity as a notable awards   
  ceremony to the Indian population as well    
  as to the viewers of Zee Network.
